{"tid":817584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"肉丸之談","createTime":"2018-09-13T12:43:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T13:51:49.000Z","uid":181997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7fcbbb33e62a402c616dc3076611d33e18e154a6","tid":817584,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"平時各位巴絲有冇食開肉丸，<br />\n屋企打邊爐有冇食開邊隻牌子好介紹，<br />\n因為我覺得喺凍肉鋪買嗰啲肉丸都唔知擺左幾耐，<br />\n又唔知係咩牌子，有時買早啲食落口怪怪地粉粉地都唔知係咩丸，有冇好介紹，最好係啲急凍嘅可以擺喺屋企雪箱個啲丫，Help<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/204302_8a22c584ed910a1ab1769f721ed72643.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F204302_8a22c584ed910a1ab1769f721ed72643.png&h=0ddf300a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3db487eb8eeb2a13ae54734486b6947f54eb71e7","tid":817584,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"街市啦屌"},{"pid":"fd74de8e064fe0e7b120fd1bd2069555036049a6","tid":817584,"uid":69083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"大埔振興肉丸"},{"pid":"a9abe5e26108f8be955ee2c9344ccda0e77dae4f","tid":817584,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3db487eb8eeb2a13ae54734486b6947f54eb71e7","tid":817584,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:45:06.000Z","msg":"街市啦屌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:47:39.000Z","msg":"唔要街市丫屌"},{"pid":"fc3681c530244c25e9a06a23b55111d3d63b61b3","tid":817584,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd74de8e064fe0e7b120fd1bd2069555036049a6","tid":817584,"uid":69083,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:45:53.000Z","msg":"大埔振興肉丸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T1